      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition and presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is immaculate, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with every system functioning exactly as intended and a complete, documented service history. This is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier example of this model that will satisfy even the most discerning collector or enthusiast.",
