    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car or a source for parts. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, large dents, and noticeable rust spots on several panels. Mechanically, the car requires immediate attention; it runs and drives but has a rough idle, a leaking exhaust, and the transmission shifts harshly. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It is sold strictly as-is.",
