      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally maintained vehicle, characterized by its consistent service history and robust mechanical integrity. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a refined exterior finish, this vehicle represents a sophisticated acquisition for the discerning driver who values reliability and long-term utility. Available now for immediate professional handover.",
      "price": 34900.0,
